span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σιλανός\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σιλανός\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Σιλανός\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Σιλανός\">ΣΙΛΑΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σιλανός\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σιλανός\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Σιλανός\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Σιλανός\">ΣΙΛΑΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἥρωες\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἥρως\">ΗΡΩΕΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀγαθοί\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἀγαθός\">ΑΓΑΘΟΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Σιλανός\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Σιλανός\">ΣΙΛΑΝΟΣ\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cspan data-text=\"Σιλανός\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Σιλανός\">ΣΙΛΑΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἥρωες\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἥρως\">ΗΡΩΕΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀγαθοί\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἀγαθός\">ΑΓΑΘΟΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text of Giustolisi as reported in SEG\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Giustolisi proposed that it was a dedication to or invovation of the divinity Silenos, but Manganaro, and Moretti (comm in SEG) instead suggest that it is a funerary aedicola for two men called Silenos, perhaps father and son, with the designation as heroes agathoi, as is common in the later Hellenistic period.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 36.0854 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Giustolisi 1981 121-122 figs.144-148r \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001947\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001947\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1992 500-501 no.IX \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001830\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001830\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[198,201,204,207,210,213,216,219],{"id":199,"html":200},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\">